ER Diagram + Data Dictionary (Logical Database Design)

Departments (1) ──< Equipment (n)
Equipment (1) ──< Maintenance (n)
Equipment (1) ──< Alerts_Issues (n)
Technicians (n) ──> Maintenance (n)        [many-to-many → resolved by Maintenance table]
Users (n) ──> Alerts_Issues (1)             [ReportedBy]
Users (n) ──> Maintenance (0,n)             [ApprovedBy – optional]


[Departments] 1────<|{ Equipment }|────1 [Alerts_Issues]
    | PK DeptID                     PK EquipmentID          PK AlertID
    | DeptName                     SerialNumber (U)        EquipmentID (FK)
    | Location                      Name                    ReportedBy → Users
    | HeadOfDept                   Category                DateReported
    |                                Manufacturer           IssueDescription
                                      Model                   Priority
                                      PurchaseDate            Status
                                      PurchaseCost
                                      WarrantyExpiry
                                      Status
                                      DeptID (FK)

[Technicians]                                        [Maintenance]
    PK TechID                                           PK MaintenanceID
    FullName                                            EquipmentID (FK)
    Contact                                             TechID (FK)
    Specialty                                           MaintenanceDate
    HireDate                                            ScheduledDate
    IsActive                                            MaintenanceType (Preventive/Corrective)
                                                        Cost
                                                        Description
                                                        Status
                                                        ApprovedBy → Users (optional)

[Users]
    PK UserID
    Username
    FullName
    Role (Admin, Technician, DeptHead, RegularUser)
    DeptID (FK)
    PasswordHash


